OL,3,CFormer police officer raised concern
OL,4,Cabout 'danger to women' colleague
OL,6,FUTV first revealed shocking details of
OL,7,Fwhat is believed to be one of the
OL,8,Fbiggest sex abuse investigations
OL,9,Fmounted by the Police Ombudsman.
OL,11,FAt its heart, a former police officer,
OL,12,Fpotential multiple victims and many
OL,13,Falleged historical crimes including an
OL,14,Fallegation of rape.
OL,16,FWe previously revealed how that former
OL,17,Fofficer's career came to an end some
OL,18,Fyears ago following an internal
OL,19,Finvestigation which included the
OL,20,Fdiscovery of alleged sexually explicit
OL,21,Fimages.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
