OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778746038
OL,3,CFormer police officer raised concern
OL,4,Cabout 'danger to women' colleague
OL,6,FA misconduct hearing was held and he
OL,7,Fwas required to resign - an option
OL,8,Fthat's since been abolished.
OL,10,FA former senior detective with
OL,11,Fknowledge of the case, who did not
OL,12,Fwant to be identified, has now spoken
OL,13,Fto UTV
OL,15,F"I personally have regrets about it.
OL,16,FMore should have been done. It should
OL,17,Fhave been done quicker.''
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
