CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778746038
OL,3,CFormer police officer raised concern
OL,4,Cabout 'danger to women' colleague
OL,6,F"The individual shouldn't have been
OL,7,Fallowed to require to resign in my
OL,8,Fopinion. The individual should have
OL,9,Fbeen dismissed and that was a mistake."
OL,11,FHe told UTV he saw the alleged
OL,12,Fsexually explicit image.
OL,14,F"I couldn't believe it when I saw it.
OL,15,FAnd when I processed it. I realised
OL,16,Fthe photo had obviously been taken by
OL,17,Fthat person who was wearing a police
OL,18,Funiform in what looked to me like a
OL,19,Fpolice establishment given the
OL,20,Fsurroundings but shocked wouldn't be
OL,21,Fthe word for it.''
OL,26,@qD@gO]
