OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778746038
OL,3,CFormer police officer raised concern
OL,4,Cabout 'danger to women' colleague
OL,6,FAnother former officer told UTV she
OL,7,Falso saw a sexually explicit image
OL,8,Fallegedly connected to the same
OL,9,Fcolleague.
OL,11,F"It was absolutely horrendous what I
OL,12,Fsaw and the implication was
OL,13,Fhorrendous. The implications were I
OL,14,Fwas in a job with standards and
OL,15,Fresponsibilities to other people and
OL,16,Fvulnerable people and what I thought
OL,17,Fwas a vulnerable person."
OL,19,FShe says she raised the issue further
OL,20,Fup the chain.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
