PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778746038
OL,3,CFormer police officer raised concern
OL,4,Cabout 'danger to women' colleague
OL,6,F''I told senior officers of what my
OL,7,Ffear was and my fear was that there
OL,8,Fwas a danger to women. I couldn't have
OL,9,Ffound the words to make it sound any
OL,10,Fbetter than what it was.''
OL,12,FShe told us she wants to know what was
OL,13,Fdone with the information she
OL,14,Fspecifically told her superiors.
OL,16,F"I thought it had gone until this
OL,17,Fstory broke and I just have those
OL,18,Fvivid flashbacks of what I saw,'' she
OL,19,Fadds
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
