OL,3,CFormer police officer raised concern
OL,4,Cabout 'danger to women' colleague
OL,6,FAsked for a comment, Chief
OL,7,FSuperintendent Stephen Murray, Head of
OL,8,FProfessional Standards said that they
OL,9,Fare fully co-operating with the
OL,10,Fombudsman.
OL,12,FIn a statement he added:``The Police
OL,13,FService of Northern Ireland welcomes
OL,14,Fthe Office for the Police Ombudsman's
OL,15,Finvestigation and will fully co-
OL,16,Foperate with it.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
