PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778746038
OL,3,CFormer police officer raised concern
OL,4,Cabout 'danger to women' colleague
OL,6,F"We expect our officers to abide by
OL,7,Fthe highest standards and follow the
OL,8,FPSNI Code of Ethics, which clearly
OL,9,Fsets out within its values framework
OL,10,Fthe expectations to behave
OL,11,Fprofessionally, lawfully, ethically
OL,12,Fand with the utmost integrity at all
OL,13,Ftimes.
OL,15,F"We will continue to ensure any
OL,16,Fwrongdoing is identified and
OL,17,Fthoroughly investigated and that there
OL,18,Fare rigorous outcomes for those found
OL,19,Fto have breached the Code of Ethics.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
