CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778746038
OL,3,CFormer police officer raised concern
OL,4,Cabout 'danger to women' colleague
OL,6,F"We will continue to encourage
OL,7,Freporting, ensure concerns are
OL,8,Fthoroughly investigated and pursue
OL,9,Frigorous outcomes where misconduct is
OL,10,Fproven."
OL,12,FThe former officer at the centre of
OL,13,Fall of this has broken his silence,
OL,14,Fthrough his solicitors.
OL,16,F"My client strenuously denies the
OL,17,Fallegations and has instructed me to
OL,18,Fcontest the charges,'' his solicitor
OL,19,FPatrick Higgins of Donnelly & Wall
OL,20,FSolicitors told UTV.
OL,26,@rD@HO]
