CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778746038
OL,3,CFormer police officer raised concern
OL,4,Cabout 'danger to women' colleague
OL,6,F"He is engaging in the current
OL,7,Fombudsman investigation and like all
OL,8,Fsuspects in the criminal justice
OL,9,Fsystem he is entitled to the
OL,10,Fpresumption of innocence. It would be
OL,11,Finappropriate to comment further at
OL,12,Fthis stage."
OL,14,FWe also put all the questions raised
OL,15,Fin our story to the Policer Ombudsman.
OL,17,FChief Executive Hugh Hume said: "Those
OL,18,Fwho have brought their concerns to us
OL,19,Fdid so in difficult circumstances.
OL,20,FTheir voices are, and will remain, at
OL,21,Fthe centre of our enquiries.
OL,26,@tD@LO]yD@aOU
