OL,3,CFormer police officer raised concern
OL,4,Cabout 'danger to women' colleague
OL,6,F"These are significant, complex and
OL,7,Fsensitive investigations, and we have
OL,8,Fallocated substantial resources to
OL,9,Fensure that they are robustly
OL,10,Fprogressed. It would be inappropriate
OL,11,Fto comment further while our enquiries
OL,12,Fare ongoing."
